Characters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"PAREO","body":"嗯哼哼哼～～～♪　\n今天是PasPale的發售活動〜〜！！\n我很早就開始在期待今天的到來了～♪","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"event143-01-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"呵呵，所以今天狀況才會這麼好啊","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event143-01-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"真受不了，一臉幸福的樣子……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event143-01-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"我也好想去現場看麻彌小姐的運棒喔～。\n下次也約我去吧，PAREO","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event143-01-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"PAREO","body":"啊，說的也是。\nPAREO總是單獨行動，不習慣邀別人一起……\n……不過，下次會記得邀請益仔學姊～♪","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"event143-01-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"拜託你啦！\n但真的讓人好羨慕喔。PasPale超級可愛的說","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"ando01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event143-01-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"PAREO","body":"對啊~~！！　大家有看過這次新單曲的封面嗎！？\n真的可愛到不行～～！！\n啊，我拿給大家看，我放在哪裡呢～……♪","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"event143-01-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"哇啊……PAREO手機裡都是PasPale的圖片……！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event143-01-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"LOCK","body":"數，數量好驚人……\nPasPale的影片跟照片源源不絕。\n啊，這張彩學姊的笑容，真好看～～！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event143-01-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"喔，真的耶","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event143-01-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"PasPale的表演總是閃閃發光，充滿了夢想，\n真的給人一種「偶像」的感覺呢。\n像這樣把快樂帶給觀眾的表演真的好厲害……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event143-01-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"嗯哼。Performance本身的確不怎麼差。\n但整體的方向，或說整個分類都和RAS完全不同就是了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"event143-01-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"也是。不過這可愛的感覺是RAS沒有的魅力吧。\n除了擁有演奏實力，同時也能展現出可愛風格。\n這種反差超棒的對吧","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event143-01-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"PAREO","body":"RAS也是兼具可愛，獨一無二的最強樂團！\nRAS的最強是無法被撼動的","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"event143-01-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"PAREO","body":"但不同於RAS，PasPale也是無敵的哦～♪\n只要看到PasPale他們五個人，心就像是緊緊被揪住一樣，\n「真的太喜歡了～」的心情會無止境地湧現出來","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"event143-01-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"LOCK","body":"PAREO同學的心情我粉懂～～！！\n我看到Popipa的時候也一樣，\n會有一股熱血從內心翻湧上來，好像充滿了力量","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event143-01-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0